name: dag_id
description: The Airflow DAG ID, e.g. doi_workflow

name: entity_id
description: A unique identifier to represent the dataset being processed.

name: data_interval_start
description: The Airflow data interval start datetime.

name: data_interval_end
description: The Airflow data interval end datetime.

name: snapshot_date
description: For datasets that release entire snapshots, the date that the snapshot was released.

name: changefile_start_date
description: The date of the first changefile in this release. For datasets that provide changefiles with inserts, updates and deletes.

name: changefile_end_date
description: The date of the last changefile in this release. For datasets that provide changefiles with inserts, updates and deletes.

name: sequence_start
description: The first sequence number of changefiles in this release. For datasets that provide changefiles with inserts, updates and deletes.

name: sequence_end
description: The last sequence number of changefiles in this release. For datasets that provide changefiles with inserts, updates and deletes.

name: extra
description: An optional JSON field for extra information.

name: created
description: The date that this record was created.

name: modified
description: The date that this record was modified.
